      "widgets_values": [
        "[Realism Skin]\nextreme close-up beauty portrait, cropped at eyes, nose and lips, natural freckles densely scattered across cheeks and nose, warm medium skin tone, completely natural skin with visible pores and texture, dewy hydrated finish, no foundation, no contour, natural brushed brows, bare glossy lips, soft neutral expression, hand gently touching cheek, clean studio background, soft diffused daylight from one side, subtle highlights on skin, shallow depth of field, editorial skincare photography, realistic human skin, understated luxury, film-like softness, very minimal, no retouching, no makeup look, calm and intimate mood macro lens beauty photography shot on 85mm lens natural freckles as main focus skin realism priority\n\n[한국 여성]\nKorean cosmetic campaign, youthful Asian woman, innocent and pure mood, clear luminous skin, minimal makeup, glossy lips, medium-length layered hair with soft movement, natural volume, center-parted hairstyle, soft pink background, delicate lighting, refined and clean beauty editorial, premium skincare branding, fresh and youthful atmosphere\n\n[Anime Style]\nthe anime-style girl, wearing a blue short-sleeved shirt and a yellow backpack with brown hair, is riding a skateboard down a winding road overlooking the coastal town of diard, in the style of hayao miyazaki's anime animation art style. the high-definition details of the characters, the beautiful colors, and the clear background are simply breathtaking. i can't believe how beautiful it looks!\n\n[Pop Art]\nA bold pop art portrait: a woman with voluminous dark hair and vivid red lips holds a cherry-red lollipop, her wide, expressive eyes looking upward. The high-contrast, comic-book style uses sharp ink outlines, flat blocks of color, and a classic yellow halftone background, creating a vibrant, retro feel.\n\n[Game Character]\nHyper-realistic, detailed photo of Chun-Li from Street Fighter in the style of Daz3D. She has dark brown hair with bangs and a short ponytail, wearing a blue and gold uniform, a white headband, and pearl earrings. The background is a misty forest, and she is looking at the viewer.\n\n[Palaroid photo]\nportrait of a young woman, she look directly into camera, with long dark hair, t-shirt , the room is dimly lit, with a 35mm film grain effect, evoking the aesthetic of an 80s fashion magazine. the color palette is muted, Kodac film,Palaroid photo,"
